    'experience_title' => 'Decades of experience and credibility at your service',
    'experience_text-1' => 'CapitureX is the result of decades of experience in investing, brokerage, and risk management. Our team of experts previously contributed to building one of Southeast Asia\'s largest retail investment platforms and now offers a platform where you can buy crypto with confidence.',
    'experience_text-2' => 'We guarantee a level playing field for all crypto investors.',
